citations:
    citation-agot-bran-i:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Bran I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Bran. Bran witnesses the execution of a Night's Watch deserter (Gared) at the holdfast. Afterward, the party finds a dead direwolf with a broken antler in her throat and five pups — later six, counting Ghost. Jon persuades Ned to let the children keep the pups."
